name: Inception
desc: The film stars Leonardo DiCaprio as a professional thief who steals information by infiltrating the subconscious of his targets. He is offered a chance to have his criminal history erased as payment for the implantation of another person's idea into a target's subconscious.

name: Avengers: Endgame
desc: the concluding film in the Infinity Saga, where the surviving Avengers, after Thanos's destructive snap, must assemble for one final time to reverse his actions and restore half of all life in the universe, which involves a perilous journey into the past using time travel via the Quantum Realm.

name: Interstellar
desc: A team of explorers travels through a wormhole in space to ensure humanity’s survival as Earth faces environmental collapse. Directed by Christopher Nolan, it blends science, emotion, and epic visuals.

name: The Dark Knight
desc: Batman faces his greatest psychological and physical test when the Joker unleashes chaos on Gotham. A gripping tale of heroism, morality, and sacrifice.

name: Titanic
desc: A young couple from different social classes fall in love aboard the doomed RMS Titanic. James Cameron’s epic blends romance and tragedy against a historical backdrop.

name: The Lion King
desc: The journey of Simba, a young lion who must embrace his destiny as king after the tragic death of his father. A timeless Disney classic about courage, family, and the circle of life.

name: Avatar
desc: On the alien world of Pandora, a paraplegic marine takes part in the Avatar program and finds himself torn between human duty and the Na’vi way of life. Known for stunning visuals and groundbreaking 3D.

name: Joker
desc: Arthur Fleck, a struggling comedian, descends into madness and transforms into the infamous Joker. A haunting character study of isolation, society, and chaos.

name: Frozen II
desc: Elsa, Anna, Kristoff, and Olaf set out beyond Arendelle to uncover the origin of Elsa’s powers and save their kingdom. A magical sequel with adventure, songs, and sisterhood at its heart.

name: Spider-Man: No Way Home
desc: Peter Parker seeks Doctor Strange’s help to restore his secret identity, but a spell goes wrong, opening the multiverse and bringing past villains into his world. An epic Spider-Man crossover.

name: The Conjuring
desc: Paranormal investigators Ed and Lorraine Warren help a family terrorized by a dark presence in their farmhouse. Based on chilling true events.

name: Insidious
desc: A couple discovers that dark spirits have trapped their comatose son in a mysterious realm called “The Further.” A terrifying journey into the world of the unknown.
